{"title":"如何通过精度判定调整音游流速 ——以《BanG Dream!》为例","slug":"如何通过精度判定调整音游流速 ——以《BanG Dream!》为例","date":"2026-03-18T09:29:56.541Z","updated":"2026-03-18T09:38:56.571Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/如何通过精度判定调整音游流速 ——以《BanG Dream!》为例.json","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://img.rubbish.press/file/2603/1773826534957_image.png","https://img.rubbish.press/file/2603/1773826544428_image.png"],"content":"<p>新手工作人员，凑友希那，冰川纱夜，今井莉莎，宇田川亚子，白金子<br>\nCIRCLE LIVE HOUSE<br>\n四叶女子大学<br>\n庆鹏女子大学<br>\n羽丘女子学园<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:zhangjq_sd@163.com\">zhangjq_sd@163.com</a><br>\n同等贡献</p>\n<!-- 以下请在href=后的双引号里填写pdf全网链接 -->\n<a href=\"https://file.rubbish.press/artical/%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%91%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%9A%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E9%9F%B3%E6%B8%B8%E6%B5%81%E9%80%9F%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A5%E3%80%8ABanG%20Dream!%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%BA%E4%BE%8B.pdf?preview\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 10px 18px; background: #2563eb; color: white; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.2s;\">\n  <svg style=\"width:18px;height:18px;fill:currentColor;\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n    <path d=\"M20 2H8c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 14H8V4h12v12zM4 6H2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14v-2H4V6zm12 6V9l-4 4-4-4v3h8z\"/>\n  </svg>\n  阅读 PDF 全文\n</a>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"摘要\">摘要</h2>\n<p>在音游玩家群体中，调整谱面流速以提升打击精度是常见操作。本文提出一种基于打击精度判定的流速调优方法，通过构建实验数据集、定义准度函数并进行拟合分析，获得最佳流速参数，从而提升全连与全完美达成的可能性。需要说明的是，本文所讨论的流速调整仅适用于打击节奏固定的音游类型，流速的变化不改变音符的实际打击时刻。</p>\n<p>关键词：音游；BanG Dream!；Roselia</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-Introduction\">1 Introduction</h2>\n<p>音游中，谱面的流速设置对玩家的打击判断具有显著影响。不同玩家根据自身反应习惯与视觉偏好，会选择不同的流速。然而，现有调整方法多依赖主观感受，缺乏系统性指导。本文以《BanG Dream!》为实验平台，尝试建立一种“复杂的”基于打击精度反馈的流速优化方法，为玩家提供可重复、可量化的调整策略。</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-Methodology\">2 Methodology</h2>\n<p>本文选取《BanG Dream!》作为实验对象，由同一玩家在控制变量的条件下，以多首曲目为样本，记录在不同流速下的打击表现。每次测试中，记录“Fast”（过早打击）与“Slow”（过晚打击）的次数，并引入准度函数对打击精度进行量化分析。准度函数定义如下：</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable width=\"100%\"><mtr><mtd width=\"50%\"></mtd><mtd><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>ν</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">S</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">l</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">o</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">w</mi></mrow><mo>−</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">F</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">a</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">s</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">t</mi></mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">S</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">l</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">o</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">w</mi></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">F</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">a</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">s</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">t</mi></mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">N</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">o</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">t</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">s</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mtd><mtd width=\"50%\"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(1)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F(\\nu) = \\frac{(\\mathrm{Slow} - \\mathrm{Fast})(\\mathrm{Slow} + \\mathrm{Fast})}{\\mathrm{Notes}} \\tag{1}\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.06366em;\">ν</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.113em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.427em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">Notes</span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\" style=\"margin-right:0.01389em;\">Slow</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">Fast</span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\" style=\"margin-right:0.01389em;\">Slow</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">Fast</span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span><span class=\"tag\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.113em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span><span class=\"mord\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>其中，(v) 为流速设置值，Notes为曲目音符总数。该函数综合考虑了打击倾向（偏向Fast或Slow）与整体精度（Fast+Slow总数），并通过音符数进行归一化处理。</p>\n<p>(F(v) &gt; 0) 表示整体偏向Slow，即流速偏快；<br>\n(F(v) &lt; 0) 表示整体偏向Fast，即流速偏慢。</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-Results-and-Discussion\">3 Results and Discussion</h2>\n<p>实验数据如下表：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>歌曲名</th>\n<th>音符数</th>\n<th>流速v</th>\n<th>Fast</th>\n<th>Slow</th>\n<th>F(v)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>-HEROIC ADVENT-</td>\n<td>509</td>\n<td>9.5</td>\n<td>16</td>\n<td>76</td>\n<td>-0.5472102161</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>FRONTIER FANTASIA</td>\n<td>425</td>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>36</td>\n<td>-0.1612470588</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>噫の花冠</td>\n<td>571</td>\n<td>10.5</td>\n<td>23</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>-0.840630473</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>熱色スターマイン</td>\n<td>529</td>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>0.680529301</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>BLACK SHOUT</td>\n<td>309</td>\n<td>11.5</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>14</td>\n<td>0.634304207</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Opera of the wasteland</td>\n<td>483</td>\n<td>12</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>99</td>\n<td>0.29192547</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>约束</td>\n<td>435</td>\n<td>10.75</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>R</td>\n<td>537</td>\n<td>10.75</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>-0.067039106</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>ONENESS</td>\n<td>445</td>\n<td>10.8</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>-0.002247191</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>SONG I AM</td>\n<td>559</td>\n<td>11.2</td>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>0.016100179</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>将上述数据绘制成散点图（见图1），可观察到流速与准度函数之间呈现明显的三次函数关系。进一步分析发现，当 (F(v)) 在 ([-1, 1]) 区间内时，流速范围集中在10.5至11.5之间，数据显示近似线性关系（尽管 (R^2) 只有0.54左右，但我们总可以近似认为这一关系成立）（见图2）。拟合直线方程为：</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable width=\"100%\"><mtr><mtd width=\"50%\"></mtd><mtd><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>ν</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>1.07833</mn><mi>ν</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>11.73915</mn></mrow></mtd><mtd width=\"50%\"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(2)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F(\\nu) = 1.07833\\nu - 11.73915 \\tag{2}\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.06366em;\">ν</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1.07833</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.06366em;\">ν</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">11.73915</span></span><span class=\"tag\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span><span class=\"mord\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>令 (F(v) = 0)，解得 v ≈10.89。以此为流速设置，重新测试《Ringing Bloom》一曲，结果Fast与Slow均为1，验证了模型的预测能力。在《FIREBIRD》中同样获得 Fast = Slow = 2，进一步支持该流速值的有效性。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.rubbish.press/file/2603/1773826534957_image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>图1 流速与准度函数之间的全局三次关系</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.rubbish.press/file/2603/1773826544428_image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>图2 流速与准度函数之间的局域线性关系</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"4-Conclusion\">4 Conclusion</h2>\n<p>然而，需注意的是，同一曲目的重复测试可能导致“手癖”现象，且符合传统认知中“菜就多练”的说法。<strong>注意：本文的实验不具有可复现性，即使是作者也无法再次准确得到上述结果。</strong></p>\n<p>本方法不仅适用于《BanG Dream!》，亦可推广至其他音游，如《舞萌DX》、《中二节奏》等。对于一般玩家，可采用“二分法”快速逼近理想流速：从10.5与11开始，逐步收敛至10.75、10.88，最终接近10.89。</p>\n<p>由于本文所使用的方法需要复杂的数学处理与数据处理，因此，<strong>我们认为本文提到的方法不具有任何实际应用价值</strong>。</p>\n<p>最后，“你们有为全连赌上一切的觉悟吗？”本文作者之一的凑友希那如是说到。</p>\n<h2 id=\"致谢\">致谢</h2>\n<p>本文测试过程中感谢Roselia乐队全员（凑友希那、冰川纱夜、今井莉莎、宇田川亚子、白金子）的演出。感谢CIRCLE提供场地与乐器支持。</p>\n<p>感谢Deepseek对本文写作提供的支持。</p>\n<p>编辑部应作者要求加入以下内容：感谢帮忙审稿的专业审稿人井芹仁菜和Rikki。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考文献\">参考文献</h2>\n<p>本文的公式均为原创，无需任何参考文献。</p>\n","more":"<p>新手工作人员，凑友希那，冰川纱夜，今井莉莎，宇田川亚子，白金子<br>\nCIRCLE LIVE HOUSE<br>\n四叶女子大学<br>\n庆鹏女子大学<br>\n羽丘女子学园<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:zhangjq_sd@163.com\">zhangjq_sd@163.com</a><br>\n同等贡献</p>\n<!-- 以下请在href=后的双引号里填写pdf全网链接 -->\n<a href=\"https://file.rubbish.press/artical/%E5%B7%B2%E5%8F%91%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87%E7%B2%BE%E5%BA%A6%E5%88%A4%E5%AE%9A%E8%B0%83%E6%95%B4%E9%9F%B3%E6%B8%B8%E6%B5%81%E9%80%9F%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E4%BB%A5%E3%80%8ABanG%20Dream!%E3%80%8B%E4%B8%BA%E4%BE%8B.pdf?preview\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 10px 18px; background: #2563eb; color: white; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 500; transition: all 0.2s;\">\n  <svg style=\"width:18px;height:18px;fill:currentColor;\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n    <path d=\"M20 2H8c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h12c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 14H8V4h12v12zM4 6H2v14c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h14v-2H4V6zm12 6V9l-4 4-4-4v3h8z\"/>\n  </svg>\n  阅读 PDF 全文\n</a>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"摘要\">摘要</h2>\n<p>在音游玩家群体中，调整谱面流速以提升打击精度是常见操作。本文提出一种基于打击精度判定的流速调优方法，通过构建实验数据集、定义准度函数并进行拟合分析，获得最佳流速参数，从而提升全连与全完美达成的可能性。需要说明的是，本文所讨论的流速调整仅适用于打击节奏固定的音游类型，流速的变化不改变音符的实际打击时刻。</p>\n<p>关键词：音游；BanG Dream!；Roselia</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-Introduction\">1 Introduction</h2>\n<p>音游中，谱面的流速设置对玩家的打击判断具有显著影响。不同玩家根据自身反应习惯与视觉偏好，会选择不同的流速。然而，现有调整方法多依赖主观感受，缺乏系统性指导。本文以《BanG Dream!》为实验平台，尝试建立一种“复杂的”基于打击精度反馈的流速优化方法，为玩家提供可重复、可量化的调整策略。</p>\n<h2 id=\"2-Methodology\">2 Methodology</h2>\n<p>本文选取《BanG Dream!》作为实验对象，由同一玩家在控制变量的条件下，以多首曲目为样本，记录在不同流速下的打击表现。每次测试中，记录“Fast”（过早打击）与“Slow”（过晚打击）的次数，并引入准度函数对打击精度进行量化分析。准度函数定义如下：</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable width=\"100%\"><mtr><mtd width=\"50%\"></mtd><mtd><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>ν</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">S</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">l</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">o</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">w</mi></mrow><mo>−</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">F</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">a</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">s</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">t</mi></mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">S</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">l</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">o</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">w</mi></mrow><mo>+</mo><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">F</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">a</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">s</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">t</mi></mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">N</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">o</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">t</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">e</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">s</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mtd><mtd width=\"50%\"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(1)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F(\\nu) = \\frac{(\\mathrm{Slow} - \\mathrm{Fast})(\\mathrm{Slow} + \\mathrm{Fast})}{\\mathrm{Notes}} \\tag{1}\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.06366em;\">ν</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.113em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:1.427em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.314em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">Notes</span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.677em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\" style=\"margin-right:0.01389em;\">Slow</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">Fast</span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\" style=\"margin-right:0.01389em;\">Slow</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord mathrm\">Fast</span></span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.686em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span><span class=\"tag\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:2.113em;vertical-align:-0.686em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span><span class=\"mord\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>其中，(v) 为流速设置值，Notes为曲目音符总数。该函数综合考虑了打击倾向（偏向Fast或Slow）与整体精度（Fast+Slow总数），并通过音符数进行归一化处理。</p>\n<p>(F(v) &gt; 0) 表示整体偏向Slow，即流速偏快；<br>\n(F(v) &lt; 0) 表示整体偏向Fast，即流速偏慢。</p>\n<h2 id=\"3-Results-and-Discussion\">3 Results and Discussion</h2>\n<p>实验数据如下表：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>歌曲名</th>\n<th>音符数</th>\n<th>流速v</th>\n<th>Fast</th>\n<th>Slow</th>\n<th>F(v)</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>-HEROIC ADVENT-</td>\n<td>509</td>\n<td>9.5</td>\n<td>16</td>\n<td>76</td>\n<td>-0.5472102161</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>FRONTIER FANTASIA</td>\n<td>425</td>\n<td>10</td>\n<td>8</td>\n<td>36</td>\n<td>-0.1612470588</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>噫の花冠</td>\n<td>571</td>\n<td>10.5</td>\n<td>23</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>-0.840630473</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>熱色スターマイン</td>\n<td>529</td>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>11</td>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>0.680529301</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>BLACK SHOUT</td>\n<td>309</td>\n<td>11.5</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>14</td>\n<td>0.634304207</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Opera of the wasteland</td>\n<td>483</td>\n<td>12</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>99</td>\n<td>0.29192547</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>约束</td>\n<td>435</td>\n<td>10.75</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>17</td>\n<td>0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>R</td>\n<td>537</td>\n<td>10.75</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>-0.067039106</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>ONENESS</td>\n<td>445</td>\n<td>10.8</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>-0.002247191</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>SONG I AM</td>\n<td>559</td>\n<td>11.2</td>\n<td>9</td>\n<td>0</td>\n<td>0.016100179</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>将上述数据绘制成散点图（见图1），可观察到流速与准度函数之间呈现明显的三次函数关系。进一步分析发现，当 (F(v)) 在 ([-1, 1]) 区间内时，流速范围集中在10.5至11.5之间，数据显示近似线性关系（尽管 (R^2) 只有0.54左右，但我们总可以近似认为这一关系成立）（见图2）。拟合直线方程为：</p>\n<p><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" display=\"block\"><semantics><mtable width=\"100%\"><mtr><mtd width=\"50%\"></mtd><mtd><mrow><mi>F</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>ν</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>1.07833</mn><mi>ν</mi><mo>−</mo><mn>11.73915</mn></mrow></mtd><mtd width=\"50%\"></mtd><mtd><mtext>(2)</mtext></mtd></mtr></mtable><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">F(\\nu) = 1.07833\\nu - 11.73915 \\tag{2}\n</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.13889em;\">F</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.06366em;\">ν</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">=</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1.07833</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.06366em;\">ν</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">−</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6444em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">11.73915</span></span><span class=\"tag\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">(</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">2</span></span><span class=\"mord\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n<p>令 (F(v) = 0)，解得 v ≈10.89。以此为流速设置，重新测试《Ringing Bloom》一曲，结果Fast与Slow均为1，验证了模型的预测能力。在《FIREBIRD》中同样获得 Fast = Slow = 2，进一步支持该流速值的有效性。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.rubbish.press/file/2603/1773826534957_image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>图1 流速与准度函数之间的全局三次关系</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://img.rubbish.press/file/2603/1773826544428_image.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>图2 流速与准度函数之间的局域线性关系</strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"4-Conclusion\">4 Conclusion</h2>\n<p>然而，需注意的是，同一曲目的重复测试可能导致“手癖”现象，且符合传统认知中“菜就多练”的说法。<strong>注意：本文的实验不具有可复现性，即使是作者也无法再次准确得到上述结果。</strong></p>\n<p>本方法不仅适用于《BanG Dream!》，亦可推广至其他音游，如《舞萌DX》、《中二节奏》等。对于一般玩家，可采用“二分法”快速逼近理想流速：从10.5与11开始，逐步收敛至10.75、10.88，最终接近10.89。</p>\n<p>由于本文所使用的方法需要复杂的数学处理与数据处理，因此，<strong>我们认为本文提到的方法不具有任何实际应用价值</strong>。</p>\n<p>最后，“你们有为全连赌上一切的觉悟吗？”本文作者之一的凑友希那如是说到。</p>\n<h2 id=\"致谢\">致谢</h2>\n<p>本文测试过程中感谢Roselia乐队全员（凑友希那、冰川纱夜、今井莉莎、宇田川亚子、白金子）的演出。感谢CIRCLE提供场地与乐器支持。</p>\n<p>感谢Deepseek对本文写作提供的支持。</p>\n<p>编辑部应作者要求加入以下内容：感谢帮忙审稿的专业审稿人井芹仁菜和Rikki。</p>\n<h2 id=\"参考文献\">参考文献</h2>\n<p>本文的公式均为原创，无需任何参考文献。</p>\n","categories":[{"name":"文章","path":"api/categories/文章.json"},{"name":"音游","path":"api/categories/音游.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"音游","path":"api/tags/音游.json"},{"name":"BanG Dream!","path":"api/tags/BanG Dream!.json"},{"name":"Roselia","path":"api/tags/Roselia.json"},{"name":"流速调整","path":"api/tags/流速调整.json"},{"name":"打击精度","path":"api/tags/打击精度.json"}]}